It can be excluded that the commissary of the 22nd district, who has since resigned from his position, who crashed a pedestrian causing his death last Tuesday, would have led in a state of drunk or turmoil, said Friday Attila Morvai, spokeswoman of the public ministry of the capital after the relative constatation was established.
