According to analysts, people who buy a building in Bulgaria are trying to change their lives, their way of life.
Most of the buyers are English but others come from France, Belgium, Spain and more and more from Romania.
On the Black Sea and in the most renowned ski stations, we traditionally meet a lot of Russian buyers.
