"The part of the amount of the damages that the customer will be paid will be determined according to the value of the premium, which will be higher the amount will be lower," said Luis Noguera, the Spanish manager of First Europa, online insurance mediator.
Another option is extended third-party insurance, so that the customer provides protection to face damages caused to third parties, but by those caused on his own car.
